{"tid":1960470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒:政府擬實施半年緊急狀態","createTime":"2020-04-06T07:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T08:13:16.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06dc9b8312e344130e51c50b01c07fd87a6f687f","tid":1960470,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/04/06/2428654_78da6f9e706603979978fa294bcca717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2F2428654_78da6f9e706603979978fa294bcca717.jpg&h=a992f5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本TBS電視台報道稱，為應對新冠病毒疫情，政府正在準備最快周二宣布緊急事態宣言，考慮實施6個月。<br />\n<br />\nTBS引述多位消息人士稱，實施範圍將涵蓋東京、東京附近三縣及大阪。在6個月的緊急狀態期間，有關地方政府將決定各自措施的施行期限。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，據《讀賣新聞》報道，首相安倍晉三最快明日宣布進入國家緊急狀態，東京都市圈、關西大阪和兵庫縣料納入措施範圍。政府希望藉此措施阻止疫情在國內蔓延。目前單計東京，累計感染人數已超過1000人。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道則稱，新措施可能周三生效。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府的疫情應對部門定於今晚召開會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2428654/日媒:政府擬實施半年緊急狀態\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2428654%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92%3A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=fae97c18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2428654/日媒:政府擬實施半年緊急狀態</a>"},{"pid":"521c05d260cf4b6596de318db490c8046cbd2eeb","tid":1960470,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"會唔會半年無新AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c95955664a9f5e41d2e8eaa7a94cd78e1ecb17","tid":1960470,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"521c05d260cf4b6596de318db490c8046cbd2eeb","tid":1960470,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"會唔會半年無新AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:06:52.000Z","msg":"之前果d J 哂？"},{"pid":"911f33076d193b409227beefff3b8ae8c819bf3b","tid":1960470,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"東京確診人數同香港差唔多<br />\n之前hea過香港依家都緊急狀態<br />\n睇來香港一係大爆發，一係777中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}